{"tid":468572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《東張西望》「探討」安宮牛黃丸功效　通訊局暫收17宗投訴","createTime":"2017-11-14T13:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T13:30:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"615bb811ecbd1f0ae9e73d076530665cb622a481","tid":468572,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171114/s00001/4617b066c4b0f12713bf520763eafe14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171114%2Fs00001%2F4617b066c4b0f12713bf520763eafe14.jpg&h=7c08e270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB節目《東張西望》在星期一（13日）一個環節中，探討安宮牛黃丸有何功效，其間清晰展示中藥品牌馬百良商標，之後亦標示馬百良提供產品贊助，惹來非議。截至今日下午5時，通訊事務管理局共收到17宗相關投訴，主要投訴內容包括不滿有關環節不斷推廣產品功效、立場偏頗、內容有誤導及失實成份，以及有植入式廣告之嫌。通訊局表示，會按既定程序處理有關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n本報正向無綫電視查詢，暫未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171114/s00001/1510657715528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171114%2Fs00001%2F1510657715528&d=QhqqYrw%2FYN%2BmI%2F2SFuNrDE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=32043eef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171114%2Fs00001%2F1510657715528&h=360b4c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171114/s00001/1510657715528</a>"},{"pid":"4112291b837af29f0f6858ce25f0f6fbcd82fd65","tid":468572,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87122ade79a7f897659b825e55c72001549531f","tid":468572,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"抵死，今日又sell m痛藥"},{"pid":"4f641858172a2fb500d7b15689c806c3c04863f9","tid":468572,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB